				</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>
			<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>
				<a href='http://blogs.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/taylorian/2015/03/03/the-sayce-bequest-michiel-de-montaigne/sayce-66_a/'><img width="150" height="133" src="http://blogs.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/taylorian/files/2015/02/SAYCE.66_a.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Josephus, Flavius. Historie des Juifs, v. 1 (1676. SAYCE.66)" aria-describedby="gallery-12-245" /></a>
			</dt>
				<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-12-245'>
